    <description>## The Demon

**The Demon**: A &quot;killer&quot; class that belongs to a Neutral Faction.
The Demon can&#39;t be converted to any faction.

**Art :** 
&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/default/original/1X/7c0b91e61da085203f26b9a62444807d0ba7b25f.png&quot; width=&quot;269&quot; height=&quot;300&quot;&gt; 

**Passive**
**Cloak Of Mithras** : Immune to death and occupation at night

**Day ability 1:**
**Haemophilia :** Increases the power of Funeral Pyre at Night (One day cooldown) - 3 uses

**Day ability 2:**
**Shape shifter** : ShapeShifter (Day) if your target dies by Execution today his class will be shown to be the demon - 1 use

Night Ability 1:
* **Funeral Pyre**: Set your target ablaze. If Haemophilia is used, anyone who comes in contact with the target is eaten alive by the half-melted corpse.

**Night room** : A bloody mess of a dormitory with torches of the highest temperature scattered inside

**Lore** : Slighted by the lack of blood sacrifices, Mithras sent the Demon to punish the Cult, and all who refuse to follow him

**Objective** : The Demon&#39;s objective is to torment and burn any player who goes against him inlcudes Blue Dragon, The unseen, The Cult and Neutral Killers.

Special thanks to B_Psycho2 for helping me out with the lore.</description>
    
